profile:
It's time to find a reliable cleaning company that won't let you down. Cleaning companies can be unreliable – have you ever had your cleaning canceled at the last minute?  Have you ever paid for a clean that wasn't what you expected it to be? Did you even notice the difference when you came home?

There is NOTHING BETTER than coming home after a day at work and the house feeling, looking, and smelling better than when you left! At Clean SPACES we know what it means to clean your space! 

If you're looking to hire your first cleaner or you want to try something new, we want you to feel comfortable making the switch. This is why we are offering our 5 for $150 on your first clean! 

Our cleaners are $35/hour per cleaner. Instant Quotes are available! Serving Calgary & Area

POST CONSTRUCTION CLEANING

Clean SPACES is dedicated to your post-construction or renovation clean-up. From Airdrie to Okotoks, from Cochrane to Strathmore, we cover the whole city on the hunt for drywall dust and window stickers. We leave your project MOVE-IN READY. Guaranteed.

We offer per-square-foot pricing, mid-project cleans, final cleans, exterior and interior cleans, and more.
